data.description: Perform and manipulate nmap scans using perl
data.PS: The following links are only valid for module list maintainers:
data.rationale:
This module was discussed over a year ago on the PAUSE list ... it
    was determined at that point that Nmap::Scanner would be the best
    name space for this as their might be other nmap-related modules
    appearing in CPAN and the Net:: namespace not appropriate as it
    dealt with generic/RFC/standard protocols.

    Applying again for this namespace in the hopes that this time my
    request will be read and honored by PAUSE/CPAN :).
